---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---
<BaseLayout title="About | Reardon Injury Law" bodyClass="body-5" currentPage="about">
  <section class="section-16" style="padding: 80px 20px; position: relative; z-index: 1;">
    <div class="w-layout-blockcontainer container-20 w-container" style="max-width: 1000px;">
      <h1 class="heading-21 sr-left" style="color: #ffffff; margin-bottom: 40px;">About Reardon Injury Law</h1>

      <div class="sr-up" style="color: #fff; font-family: 'Open Sans', sans-serif; font-size: 18px; line-height: 1.8; margin-bottom: 50px;">
        <p style="margin-bottom: 25px;">At Reardon Injury Law, we believe that every accident victim deserves personalized attention, aggressive representation, and transparent communication from start to finish. We&#8217;re not a giant call-center firm &#8212; when you work with us, you work directly with an attorney who cares about your case.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="sr-right" style="background: linear-gradient(180deg, #1e1e1f 0%, #141415 100%); border: 1px solid rgba(238, 186, 107, 0.3); border-radius: 16px; padding: 50px; margin-bottom: 50px;">
        <h2 style="color: #ffffff; font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; font-size: 32px; margin-bottom: 25px;">Meet John Reardon</h2>
        <p style="color: #fff; font-family: 'Open Sans', sans-serif; font-size: 17px; line-height: 1.8; margin-bottom: 20px;">John Reardon brings a unique perspective to personal injury law. As a <strong style="color: #eeba6b;">retired chiropractor with over 20 years of clinical experience</strong>, he understands injuries at a deeper level than most attorneys.</p>
        <p style="color: #fff; font-family: 'Open Sans', sans-serif; font-size: 17px; line-height: 1.8; margin-bottom: 20px;">During his two decades treating accident victims, John saw firsthand how insurance companies and unethical medical providers took advantage of injured people. This drove him to become an attorney &#8212; so he could protect clients from both sides of the equation.</p>
        <p style="color: #fff; font-family: 'Open Sans', sans-serif; font-size: 17px; line-height: 1.8;">His medical background allows him to understand the true extent of your injuries, communicate effectively with your doctors, and ensure you receive the treatment and compensation you deserve.</p>
      </div>

      <h2 class="sr-up" style="color: #ffffff; font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; font-size: 28px; margin-bottom: 30px;">What Sets Us Apart</h2>

      <div class="sr-stagger" style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); gap: 25px; margin-bottom: 50px;">
        <div class="practice-area-card sr-child">
          <h3><img class="practice-area-icon" src="/images/icons/medical-expertise.svg" alt="Medical expertise icon"> Medical Expertise</h3>
          <p>John Reardon spent two decades treating accident victims. He knows how injuries progress, what treatment you need, and how to document your case properly.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="practice-area-card sr-child">
          <h3><img class="practice-area-icon" src="/images/icons/personal-attention.svg" alt="Personal attention icon"> Personal Attention</h3>
          <p>Your case is never just a file number to us. You&#8217;ll work directly with an attorney who knows your name, understands what you&#8217;re going through, and stays on top of every detail from day one.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="practice-area-card sr-child">
          <h3><img class="practice-area-icon" src="/images/icons/aggressive-representation.svg" alt="Aggressive representation icon"> Aggressive Representation</h3>
          <p>Insurance companies know we&#8217;re willing to go to trial. That reputation helps us negotiate better settlements for our clients.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="practice-area-card sr-child">
          <h3><img class="practice-area-icon" src="/images/icons/transparent-communication.svg" alt="Transparent communication icon"> Transparent Communication</h3>
          <p>We keep you informed at every step. No surprises, no runaround. You&#8217;ll always know exactly where your case stands.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="sr-up" style="text-align: center; padding: 50px 40px; background: linear-gradient(145deg, #1e1e1f 0%, #141415 100%); border: 1px solid rgba(238, 186, 107, 0.3); border-radius: 16px; position: relative; overflow: hidden;">
        <div style="position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; right: 0; height: 3px; background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, #eeba6b, transparent);"></div>
        <h3 style="color: #ffffff; font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; font-size: 26px; margin-bottom: 12px; font-weight: 700;">Ready to Discuss Your Case?</h3>
        <p style="color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8); font-family: 'Open Sans', sans-serif; font-size: 17px; margin-bottom: 28px;">Free consultation. No fees unless we win.</p>
        <a href="tel:6575227122" style="display: inline-block; background: linear-gradient(180deg, #eeba6b 0%, #d4a84f 100%); color: #141415; padding: 16px 44px; border-radius: 10px; font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; font-weight: 700; text-decoration: none; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.5px; transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;">Call (657) 522-7122</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
